original_title: Framing Floors and Stairs with Larry Haun
overview: In Framing Floors and Stairs, Larry Haun and his brother Joe frame the floor of a basic 1,600 square foot house. They take you step-by-step through the entire process, showing you practical ways to organize tasks, streamline procedures, and handle all the right tools and materials efficiently.
title: Framing Floors and Stairs with Larry Haun
